OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FThe bereaved families of the
OL,8,FNottingham attacks have criticised the
OL,9,FCity Council over a lack of a
OL,10,Fpermanent memorial to their loved ones.
OL,12,FAt a media conference on Monday, June
OL,13,F8th, which followed the conclusion of
OL,14,Fevidence at the inquiry, they
OL,15,Fdescribed the lack of contact and
OL,16,Fprogress as a "kick in the teeth."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FThey claimed that they were "appalled
OL,8,Fby Nottingham City Council" and were
OL,9,Fcynical about the MPs presence in
OL,10,F2023, labelling it as "photo-
OL,11,Fopportunities".
OL,13,FGrandfather Ian Coates and University
OL,14,Fof Nottingham students Barnaby Webber,
OL,15,Ffrom Taunton in Somerset and Grace
OL,16,FO'Malley-Kumar from London, were all
OL,17,Fstabbed by paranoid schizophrenic
OL,18,FValdo Calocane.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FThe triple killer was sectioned four
OL,8,Ftimes before he also seriously injured
OL,9,FWayne Birkett, Sharon Miller and
OL,10,FMarcin Gawronski with a van during his
OL,11,Fviolent rampage in Nottingham on June
OL,12,F13th, 2023.
OL,14,FThe families of the three victims of
OL,15,Fthe Nottingham attacks say "every
OL,16,Fsingle agency failed" in their press
OL,17,Fconference.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FThey also noted that while the council
OL,8,Fquickly offered promises immediately
OL,9,Ffollowing the attacks, little to no
OL,10,Ffollow-up occurred.
OL,12,FThe City Council, along with
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police and the NHS,
OL,14,Fpreviously had to apologise after
OL,15,Fstaff inappropriately accessed
OL,16,Fsensitive and private data and records
OL,17,Frelated to the attacks and the
OL,18,Fdeceased victims.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FWhen asked about the plans for
OL,8,Fremembrance for the anniversary this
OL,9,Fweekend at the conference, James
OL,10,FCoates, son of Ian Coates, said:
OL,11,F"We're still waiting to hear back
OL,12,Fabout the teddy bears and all the
OL,13,Fstuff that was left on the 13th June
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,F"We're three years down the line, and
OL,17,Fwe still haven't heard back, so that
OL,18,Fjust shows really."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FHi brother Lee Coates added: "The
OL,8,Flocal MPs, they got their picture at
OL,9,Fthe time, back in 2023, and that's
OL,10,Fabout as far as it extended."
OL,12,FClaiming the council have not done
OL,13,Fmuch beyond getting MPs " photo-
OL,14,Fopportunities", Grace O'Malley-Kumar's
OL,15,Fmother, Dr. Sinead O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,16,Fdoubled down, saying: "The council, I
OL,17,Fthink, arranged their own little trip
OL,18,Fto church at the first anniversary,
OL,19,Fwhich they didn't even bother to
OL,20,Fnotify us.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,F"I think they just wanted a photo
OL,8,Fopportunity.
OL,10,F"Absolutely nothing has been arranged.
OL,12,F"It's not apparent to us that the
OL,13,Fcouncil have any intention of doing
OL,14,Fanything, so it might be left up to
OL,15,Fourselves."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FThe parents of Grace O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,8,FDr Sanjoy Kumar and Dr Sinead O'Malley-
OL,9,FKumar, claim any sort of memorial for
OL,10,Ftheir daughter Grace, Ian Coates and
OL,11,FBarnaby Webber will likely need to be
OL,12,Fsorted out between themselves.
OL,14,FLee Coates claimed that outside of the
OL,15,Fwalks organised by the families,
OL,16,Flittle was done by the council to
OL,17,Fremember the lives lost and affected.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FDr. Sinead O'Malley-Kumar added: "We
OL,8,Fwouldn't be holding our breaths for
OL,9,Fthe council or anybody in Nottingham
OL,10,Fto do anything for us. Don't get me
OL,11,Fwrong, some of our best friends live
OL,12,Fin Nottingham, the Coates being them."
OL,14,F"The people of Nottingham are lovely.
OL,15,FThe council, the members of
OL,16,Fparliament, they haven't reached out
OL,17,Fto us, they never have done."
OL,19,F"We shouldn't have to go to a public
OL,20,Fstreet to remember the victims of the
OL,21,FNottingham attacks.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,F"They should have something a little
OL,8,Fmore concrete to remember, and to be a
OL,9,Fmemorial for people to be able to take
OL,10,Fa moment."
OL,12,FGrace's father, Dr. Sanjoy Kumar, also
OL,13,Fexpressed the same sentiments towards
OL,14,Fnot having a permanent place for a
OL,15,Fmemorial.
OL,17,FHe said: "I think this is a case that
OL,18,Fis going to change the country. I
OL,19,Fthink this is a case that will make
OL,20,Four country safer for families.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,F"Our tragedies have played out in
OL,8,Fpublic.
OL,10,F"Not to have a somewhere that can be
OL,11,Fdedicated to, it's an utter shame,
OL,12,Fbecause I think this is a case that
OL,13,Fwill make a difference to all of us."
OL,15,FLee Coates says that it's a "shame"
OL,16,Fthe council has failed to provide a
OL,17,Fmemorial for their father Ian, and
OL,18,FBarnaby and Grace, saying that this
OL,19,Fhasn't just impacted their families
OL,20,Fand the families of the survivors, but
OL,21,Fso many other people across the city.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FHe believes that the people of
OL,8,FNottingham deserve more: "I feel for
OL,9,Fthem. There should be something
OL,10,Facknowledgment-wise from the council."
OL,12,FIan Coates' son, Darren Coates, shares
OL,13,Fthe same sentiments of the family,
OL,14,Fsaying: "It happened in our city,
OL,15,Fwe've been really busy the last few
OL,16,Fmonths.
OL,18,F"The last thing we've been trying to
OL,19,Fthink about is what we're going to do
OL,20,Fto mark the day.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,F"That should have been in place for us.
OL,9,F"I'm from Nottingham, and I find it
OL,10,Fappalling that Nottingham City Council
OL,11,Fhaven't done something.
OL,13,F"It's next weekend, this is appalling
OL,14,Ffrom Nottingham City Council."
OL,16,FThe family are now focused not only on
OL,17,Fcalling for accountability and action
OL,18,Fagainst the public servants who failed
OL,19,Fthem, they are also now anxiously
OL,20,Fmaking their own arrangements for this
OL,21,Fanniversary of losing their loved ones.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FThe Webber family have chosen not to
OL,8,Fgo to Nottingham and instead spend the
OL,9,Fanniversary of that tragic day in
OL,10,FCornwall - a place close to their
OL,11,Fson's heart.
OL,13,FBarnaby Webber's mother, Emma, said:
OL,14,F"I find it really difficult to go to
OL,15,FNottingham, because even the drive
OL,16,Fin... It's certainly not the people.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,F"To anyone who is in Nottingham, if
OL,8,Fyou see these guys (the Coates and the
OL,9,FO'Malley-Kumars), or you want to light
OL,10,Fa candle or say a prayer, please do,
OL,11,Ffor the three of them.
OL,13,F"Because I know it's a great city, and
OL,14,Fhow much Barney loved it."
OL,26,@pD@TpmqD@Ppn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/17
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
