OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781118693
OL,3,CFamily of Nottingham attacks victims
OL,4,Csay council's efforts have been
OL,5,C'appalling'
OL,7,FNottingham City Council didn't
OL,8,Fdirectly answer the questions about
OL,9,Fplans for a permanent memorial;
OL,10,Finstead, Council Leader, Cllr Neghat
OL,11,FKhan, issued this statement: "The
OL,12,FCouncil will reflect on the lessons
OL,13,Fand recommendations from the Inquiry
OL,14,Fwhen they are published.
OL,16,F"Nottingham will never forget and our
OL,17,Fthoughts are with the families of Ian,
OL,18,FBarnaby and Grace and those who
OL,19,Fsuffered injuries on the tragic day in
OL,20,FJune 2023."
OL,26,@sD@^OU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/17
